{
  "book": "2nephi",
  "bookName": "2 Nephi",
  "chapter": 29,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 292.016,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.368,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, there shall be many\u2014",
      "verse": "29:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 2.548,
      "end": 7.192,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "at that day when I shall proceed to do a marvelous work among them,",
      "verse": "29:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 7.372,
      "end": 9.973,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I may remember my covenants",
      "verse": "29:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 10.153,
      "end": 12.986,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which I have made unto the children of men,",
      "verse": "29:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 13.166,
      "end": 16.37,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I may set my hand again the second time",
      "verse": "29:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 16.55,
      "end": 20.497,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to recover my people, which are of the house of Israel;",
      "verse": "29:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 21.177,
      "end": 24.149,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And also, that I may remember the promises",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 24.329,
      "end": 26.697,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which I have made unto thee, Nephi,",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 26.877,
      "end": 28.642,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also unto thy father,",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 28.822,
      "end": 31.051,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I would remember your seed;",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 31.231,
      "end": 34.342,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that the words of your seed should proceed forth",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 34.522,
      "end": 36.844,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "out of my mouth unto your seed;",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 37.024,
      "end": 40.368,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my words shall hiss forth unto the ends of the earth,",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 40.548,
      "end": 42.731,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for a standard unto my people,",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 42.911,
      "end": 45.512,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are of the house of Israel;",
      "verse": "29:2",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 46.192,
      "end": 48.421,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And because my words shall hiss forth\u2014",
      "verse": "29:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 48.601,
      "end": 50.505,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "many of the Gentiles shall say:",
      "verse": "29:3",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 50.685,
      "end": 52.635,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "A Bible! A Bible!",
      "verse": "29:3",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 52.815,
      "end": 54.533,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "We have got a Bible,",
      "verse": "29:3",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 54.713,
      "end": 56.849,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and there cannot be any more Bible.",
      "verse": "29:3",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 57.529,
      "end": 59.433,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But thus saith the Lord God:",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 59.613,
      "end": 60.681,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O fools,",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 60.861,
      "end": 62.394,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall have a Bible;",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 62.574,
      "end": 65.128,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it shall proceed forth from the Jews,",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 65.308,
      "end": 67.212,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "mine ancient covenant people.",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 67.392,
      "end": 69.25,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And what thank they the Jews",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 69.43,
      "end": 72.031,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the Bible which they receive from them?",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 72.211,
      "end": 73.929,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, what do the Gentiles mean?",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 74.109,
      "end": 76.106,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Do they remember the travails,",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 76.286,
      "end": 77.679,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the labors,",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 77.859,
      "end": 79.67,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the pains of the Jews,",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 79.85,
      "end": 81.893,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their diligence unto me,",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 82.073,
      "end": 84.813,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in bringing forth salvation unto the Gentiles?",
      "verse": "29:4",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 85.493,
      "end": 86.886,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O ye Gentiles,",
      "verse": "29:5",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 87.066,
      "end": 89.016,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "have ye remembered the Jews,",
      "verse": "29:5",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 89.196,
      "end": 91.146,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "mine ancient covenant people?",
      "verse": "29:5",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 91.326,
      "end": 93.555,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Nay; but ye have cursed them,",
      "verse": "29:5",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 93.735,
      "end": 95.36,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and have hated them,",
      "verse": "29:5",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 95.54,
      "end": 97.955,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and have not sought to recover them.",
      "verse": "29:5",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 98.135,
      "end": 101.85,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, I will return all these things upon your own heads;",
      "verse": "29:5",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 102.03,
      "end": 104.677,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I the Lord have not forgotten my people.",
      "verse": "29:5",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 105.357,
      "end": 107.215,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Thou fool, that shall say:",
      "verse": "29:6",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 107.395,
      "end": 109.345,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "A Bible, we have got a Bible,",
      "verse": "29:6",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 109.525,
      "end": 111.011,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we need no more Bible.",
      "verse": "29:6",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 111.191,
      "end": 113.931,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Have ye obtained a Bible save it were by the Jews?",
      "verse": "29:6",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 114.611,
      "end": 117.537,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Know ye not that there are more nations than one?",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 117.717,
      "end": 119.203,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Know ye not that I,",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 119.383,
      "end": 120.823,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Lord your God,",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 121.003,
      "end": 122.582,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "have created all men,",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 122.762,
      "end": 126.849,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that I remember those who are upon the isles of the sea;",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 127.029,
      "end": 129.444,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that I rule in the heavens above",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 129.624,
      "end": 131.342,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and in the earth beneath;",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 131.522,
      "end": 135.098,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I bring forth my word unto the children of men,",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 135.278,
      "end": 138.064,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even upon all the nations of the earth?",
      "verse": "29:7",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 138.744,
      "end": 140.277,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore murmur ye,",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 140.457,
      "end": 143.197,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because that ye shall receive more of my word?",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 143.377,
      "end": 146.396,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Know ye not that the testimony of two nations",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 146.576,
      "end": 149.084,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "is a witness unto you that I am God,",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 149.264,
      "end": 152.236,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I remember one nation like unto another?",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 152.416,
      "end": 154.506,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, I speak the same words",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 154.686,
      "end": 157.147,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto one nation like unto another.",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 157.327,
      "end": 159.928,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And when the two nations shall run together",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 160.108,
      "end": 163.73,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the testimony of the two nations shall run together also.",
      "verse": "29:8",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 164.41,
      "end": 166.871,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I do this that I may prove unto many",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 167.051,
      "end": 170.255,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I am the same yesterday, today, and forever;",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 170.435,
      "end": 172.571,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that I speak forth my words",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 172.751,
      "end": 174.655,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to mine own pleasure.",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 174.835,
      "end": 177.203,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And because that I have spoken one word",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 177.383,
      "end": 180.216,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye need not suppose that I cannot speak another;",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 180.396,
      "end": 182.579,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for my work is not yet finished;",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 182.759,
      "end": 185.36,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither shall it be until the end of man,",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 185.54,
      "end": 188.419,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither from that time henceforth and forever.",
      "verse": "29:9",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 189.099,
      "end": 191.514,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, because that ye have a Bible",
      "verse": "29:10",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 191.694,
      "end": 194.852,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye need not suppose that it contains all my words;",
      "verse": "29:10",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 195.032,
      "end": 198.84,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither need ye suppose that I have not caused more to be written.",
      "verse": "29:10",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 199.52,
      "end": 201.192,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For I command all men,",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 201.372,
      "end": 203.88,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "both in the east and in the west,",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 204.06,
      "end": 206.15,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and in the north, and in the south,",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 206.33,
      "end": 208.28,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and in the islands of the sea,",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 208.46,
      "end": 212.129,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they shall write the words which I speak unto them;",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 212.309,
      "end": 215.003,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for out of the books which shall be written",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 215.183,
      "end": 216.669,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will judge the world,",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 216.849,
      "end": 218.846,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "every man according to their works,",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 219.026,
      "end": 221.255,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to that which is written.",
      "verse": "29:11",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 221.935,
      "end": 224.443,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, I shall speak unto the Jews",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 224.623,
      "end": 226.248,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall write it;",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 226.428,
      "end": 229.261,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I shall also speak unto the Nephites",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 229.441,
      "end": 231.066,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall write it;",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 231.246,
      "end": 235.797,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I shall also speak unto the other tribes of the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 235.977,
      "end": 237.649,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which I have led away,",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 237.829,
      "end": 239.454,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall write it;",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 239.634,
      "end": 242.978,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I shall also speak unto all nations of the earth",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 243.158,
      "end": 244.691,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall write it.",
      "verse": "29:12",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 245.371,
      "end": 250.015,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it shall come to pass that the Jews shall have the words of the Nephites,",
      "verse": "29:13",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 250.195,
      "end": 253.632,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Nephites shall have the words of the Jews;",
      "verse": "29:13",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 253.812,
      "end": 259.338,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Nephites and the Jews shall have the words of the lost tribes of Israel;",
      "verse": "29:13",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 259.518,
      "end": 264.255,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the lost tribes of Israel shall have the words of the Nephites and the Jews.",
      "verse": "29:13",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 264.935,
      "end": 267.396,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it shall come to pass that my people,",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 267.576,
      "end": 270.13,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are of the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 270.31,
      "end": 271.889,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall be gathered home",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 272.069,
      "end": 274.298,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the lands of their possessions;",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 274.478,
      "end": 277.032,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my word also shall be gathered in one.",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 277.212,
      "end": 280.277,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I will show unto them that fight against my word",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 280.457,
      "end": 282.036,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and against my people,",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 282.216,
      "end": 284.863,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who are of the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 285.043,
      "end": 286.483,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I am God,",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 286.663,
      "end": 288.799,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that I covenanted with Abraham",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 288.979,
      "end": 291.347,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I would remember his seed forever.",
      "verse": "29:14",
      "lineIndex": 109
    }
  ]
}